    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document defines the format of Uniform Resource Identifiers (URIs) to identify resources that are reached using Internet mail.  It adds better internationalization and compatibility with Internationalized Resource Identifiers (IRIs; RFC 3987) to the previous syntax of 'mailto' URIs (RFC 2368). [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
